name: SmartSurvey
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: smart survey
des: This is a skill which we made through which user can fill or give feed back feedback on range of surveys. In order to envoke this we user needs to say 'Alexa open smart survey'. This is connected through a service which and shows the user option for survey to fill. The response of the user for a given survey survey is stored on back end data base for further analysis or improvement.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
